Equipment {@st59b} {nl} {@st59s}- Hairstyle/Costume: Equipment to change a characters appearance {nl} - Weapon: Can use one-handed or two-handed weapons {nl} (sub-weapon/shield can be worn with a one-handed weapon) {nl} - Armor: Top, Pants, Gloves, Shoes {nl} - Accessories: Can wear 1 Necklace and 2 Bracelets {nl} {/}
{@st42b} Show only recipes with sufficient materials {/}

{@st59b} Adventure Journal {nl}{@st59s}- Game progress is recorded in the Adventure Journal {nl} - Get Adventure Index through items, monsters, crafting, map navigation, game progress {nl}    Adventure Index : Sum of all indices {nl}    Character : 5 points per level and class level {nl}    Item : Equipment: Level X 10 points, Book : 10 points, Others : 1 point {nl}    Monster : 10 points per monster (Boss: 50 points) {nl}    Map : 1 point per 10% {nl}    Quest: 1 point per quest {nl}    Achievement: Varies by achievement {nl}    Crafting : 10 points {nl}    Collection : Deck 5 points, 45 points when complete {nl} - Receive rewards from town NPC depending on the Adventure Index {/}
